Plot: The desert planet of Arrakis has begun to grow green and lush. The life-giving spice is abundant. The nine-year-old royal twins, possesing their father's supernatural powers, are being groomed as Messiahs. But there are those who think the Imperium does not need messiahs...
Characters: Leto Atreides II, Muad'dib, Stilgar, Vladimir Harkonnen, Duncan Idaho, Paul Atreides, Alia Atreides, Lady Jessica, Gurney Halleck
